{"tid":277087,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【人頭有價】22歲「零履歷」少女 月薪6萬 做主板企新CEO","createTime":"2017-06-09T10:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T11:06:55.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52a20f2e620cea8f1365a0ed461c80a34c095533","tid":277087,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"「人頭」有價呀！最新有上市公司，竟然委任一個幾乎冇履歷嘅22歲少女去做行政總裁！<br />\n<br />\n共享經濟集團（1178）最新公佈，委任22歲孟筱茜為集團行政總裁，自6月7日起，即係兩日前已經生效！有睇開通告嘅都知，多數公司委任新高層時，都會喺通告上晒冷式盡寫新高層履歷，咁大家一齊睇吓呢位小妮子嘅履歷：<br />\n<br />\n「孟筱茜女士，22歲，為恒富控股（643）之業務拓展經理，主管企業之整體發展及控制投資風險於合適水平。<br />\n<br />\n孟女士亦已獲委任為下列本集團成員公司之董事︰<br />\n1. ECrent (Hong Kong) Limited；<br />\n2. ECrent (HK) Company Limited；<br />\n3. 怡嘉投資有限公司；及<br />\n4. 中國信發集團有限公司。」<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n連孟筱茜持有咩大學學位都冇披露，到底係點解呢？孟小姐打呢份工，月薪60000蚊呀，年薪達72萬。<br />\n<br />\n公司同時公佈，委任陳雅文為新執董兼首席財務官，呢位陳雅文同樣只係23歲，月薪同樣係60000蚊。佢係主要股東陳春暉個女，而通告上，陳雅文嘅履歷表就多啲嘢睇，至少你知佢係曼徹斯特大學畢業，同埋曾做過深圳市南銀投資副總裁，仲有&hellip;喺中國信達（香港）做過實習。<br />\n<br />\n由健康食品股轉型嘅共享經濟集團，呢間上市公司做嘅業務有幾共享，大家未必知，但旗下嘅ECrent，有家就可能有啲印象。公司曾公佈出租寵物引起爭議，最終計劃煞停；其後與香港7-11合作推出出租充電器。共享經濟今年3月公佈，向中民投附屬中民國際資本發配售10億新股的協議失效，股價插水式下挫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1496992228_1171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1496992228_1171.jpg&h=a1070ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1496983003_b4f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1496983003_b4f2.jpg&h=ca3bbd02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56804738&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56804738%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&d=hvP%2BnfRiAtt%2BDbsVJPhKghFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=d2a5a308\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56804738%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&h=b4f0e13c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56804738&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609</a>"},{"pid":"02c75ae0bc0be6e2543766610890707e3650d2d4","tid":277087,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:24:08.000Z","msg":"妖股都係要黎洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1829ad9b825d60c3a290cfbdc78630ab1afd464","tid":277087,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"呃錢冇極限 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ca537f9b49fbff37a691122eec763d722f6275","tid":277087,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"拎正牌出糧比條女"},{"pid":"ab2fc05f3b5cf33beb2168c5b29773258184ac1c","tid":277087,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fc4009ff22b69195443e4750037424ac6938ca","tid":277087,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"乜柒都叫「共享」,租就租啦，改個「共享」又扮新概念"},{"pid":"0f565a3e46c3b5834f694942ed7e8df6ce593011","tid":277087,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"105577b94171c564ab577f3d4e6eac9eb1c1738a","tid":277087,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"做雞做到上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33caeda6e2f05f4c214115d0e8db58a1b7aa3a44","tid":277087,"uid":82532,"